      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOCO MISS (5) won by a space last time scoring by 6 lengths at this track in a handy 18.03. Has a good record here including three wins. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. MISS TWIX (1) did a good job to finish third last time out over 320m at this track (18.53) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot. Can feature with the right run. TRUE PROMISES (3) was fast into stride from box six to score two back (18.39) then jumped from the same draw last time but got further back when 6th at this track (18.81). Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from four starts. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. ICE ON FIRE (2) finished in the placings last start and deserves some thought.",
